{"tid":2029744,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"黃明志YouTube達10億觀看","createTime":"2020-05-22T11:29:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T11:30:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2de26b277b0b3d0862b053c8262d1adbf524b564","tid":2029744,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:29:44.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200522/WT73YALWUMW6FV47WU5AJOU6HI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200522%2FWT73YALWUMW6FV47WU5AJOU6HI%2F&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSjBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=199ac0dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200522%2FWT73YALWUMW6FV47WU5AJOU6HI%2F&h=04f45db2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200522/WT73YALWUMW6FV47WU5AJOU6HI/</a><br />\n<br />\n黃明志YouTube達10億觀看<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200522/large/1590068862_60a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200522%2Flarge%2F1590068862_60a0.jpg&h=26e0441a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃明志新歌《我們的海闊天空》MV被指撐香港的抗爭運動，早前在內地下架。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n面對強權日益嚴重地打壓創作及新聞自由，逆權相關題材的視聽產品顯得更有市場。向來敢言的馬來西亞創作歌手黃明志，前日在fb宣佈喜訊，表示其YouTube Channel已經有十億觀看人數，感謝大家由2006年開始支持至今，他說：「14年過去了，這裏已經多了好多朋友，這個頻道已經變成了我發佈作品，分享生活，傳播自由思想，對抗種族歧視，以及和惡勢力抗爭的平台。」他續說：「創作無罪，造反有理，自由媒體萬歲！」黃明志去年公開支持香港的逆權運動，早前又推出新歌《我們的海闊天空》，因MV被指有黑衣示威者場面，歌曲最後在內地被禁。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：阿澤斥通訊局離譜<br />\n<br />\n另外，描述本土派政治人物梁天琦心路歷程的紀錄片《地厚天高》，日前成功在50個國家的 iTunes Store上架，未到一個星期，前日已成為銷售排行榜第一位。之前由於《地》。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n採訪：何永寧<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200522/large/1590068861_288a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200522%2Flarge%2F1590068861_288a.jpg&h=7f591fd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紀錄片《地厚天高》講述現仍身陷囹圄的梁天琦由旺角騷亂、新東補選到判刑前的心路歷程。劇照"},{"pid":"1562542ff3791d2ffb9efd99d634584c79b3ec2e","tid":2029744,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:30:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vugdAiZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvugdAiZ.gif&h=7083d6a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z86kZLF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz86kZLF.jpg&h=c11f4c24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7QMX1Y0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7QMX1Y0.jpg&h=ff057371&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔出嘅話</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MyDSQSo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMyDSQSo.gif&h=31b5d12e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}